track_notes:
From the italian side. In summer easy trail. 
You can choice to do only 1 . Good view on the sea.

Long walk to this summit (passing next Mt Bertrand).
Plenty room to park at the village and also on summit for antenna. Since the big Alex storm, the path may be affected!

Park at 1600 m  strada provinciale 97. But you can reach 1900 m on unpaved road only with 4x4 cars.
YOU MUST PAY TOLL 15 EUROS X ROAD .
We prefer drink 3 beers with that money!
track_title: EASY  GOOD TRACK  2 summit in a day
